Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.generic_scpi.SCPIMultimeter, ['CONF?', 'CONF?',
    'CONF?', 'CONF:FRES MIN', 'CONF?', 'CONF:CURR:DC 1.0'], [
    'CURR:AC +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06', 'CURR:AC AUTO,+3.000000E-06',
    'FRES +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06', 'CURR:DC +1.000000E+01,+3.000000E-06']
    ) as dmm:
    unit_eq(dmm.input_range, 10.0 * u.amp)
    assert dmm.input_range == dmm.InputRange.automatic
    dmm.input_range = dmm.InputRange.minimum
    dmm.input_range = 1 * u.amp
